    <item>
      <title>佳士得称黑客窃取了部分客户的护照数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/christie-says-hackers-accessed-passport-data-from-some-clients</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据一份发送给客户的备忘录，针对佳士得的黑客组织窃取了客户向拍卖行提供的用于验证身份的信息，包括姓名、出生日期和护照号码。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/christie-says-hackers-accessed-passport-data-from-some-clients</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:59:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受过度扩张和低需求影响，电子杂货商申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/e-grocer-hurt-by-overexpansion-and-low-demand-files-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电子杂货初创公司 Takeoff Technologies Inc. 已申请破产，原因是其业务扩张过快，而网上杂货订单需求却不断减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/e-grocer-hurt-by-overexpansion-and-low-demand-files-bankruptcy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:58:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>KKR 220 亿欧元收购意大利电信交易获欧盟批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/kkr-s-22-billion-telecom-italia-deal-wins-unconditional-eu-nod</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR &amp; Co. 以 220 亿欧元（238 亿美元）收购意大利电信 (Telecom Italia SpA) 固定电话网络的提议已获得欧盟早期批准，为这家前电话垄断企业放弃其最有价值资产的控制权铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/kkr-s-22-billion-telecom-italia-deal-wins-unconditional-eu-nod</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:20:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊隆·马斯克同意在美国证券交易委员会的 Twitter 收购调查中作证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/elon-musk-agrees-to-testify-in-sec-probe-of-twitter-acquisition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克已同意在美国证券交易委员会对其 2022 年收购曾被称为 Twitter 的社交媒体平台的调查中作证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/elon-musk-agrees-to-testify-in-sec-probe-of-twitter-acquisition</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:07:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诉讼称马斯克和摩根士丹利“隐瞒”购买 Twitter 股票的行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/musk-morgan-stanley-hid-twitter-stock-purchases-lawsuit-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据股东诉讼称，埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 于 2022 年初秘密收购了 Twitter Inc. 的大量股份，并最终将其买下。他是在摩根士丹利 (Morgan Stanley) 一位财富经理的帮助下做到这一点的，这位经理为这位亿万富翁提供了如何避免引起大盘警觉的建议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/musk-morgan-stanley-hid-twitter-stock-purchases-lawsuit-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 03:35:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前景不佳导致 Salesforce 股价暴跌 2008 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/salesforce-gives-weak-sales-outlook-with-slowdown-fears-growing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Salesforce Inc. 预计季度销售增幅将创历史新低，随后其股价出现近 20 年来最大跌幅，这再次引发了人们对该公司将在人工智能热潮中落后的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/salesforce-gives-weak-sales-outlook-with-slowdown-fears-growing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:11:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
